@SearchService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5050

### Search products by query
GET {{SearchService_HostAddress}}/api/search/products?q=gaming&page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

###

### Search all products (no query)
GET {{SearchService_HostAddress}}/api/search/products
Accept: application/json

###

### Get all products with pagination
GET {{SearchService_HostAddress}}/api/search/products/all?page=1&pageSize=5
Accept: application/json

###

### Get product by ID from search index
GET {{SearchService_HostAddress}}/api/search/products/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Search for "laptop" products
GET {{SearchService_HostAddress}}/api/search/products?q=laptop
Accept: application/json

###

### Search with fuzzy matching (typo in "laptop")
GET {{SearchService_HostAddress}}/api/search/products?q=laptoop
Accept: application/json

###

### Search in description
GET {{SearchService_HostAddress}}/api/search/products?q=gaming RTX
Accept: application/json

###
